        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Gird thyself; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the custom being to wear long garments, they were not so fit to go about any business until they had girt their garments to them; hence Jeremiah is commanded to get a girdle about him, ",
        "children": []
