      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Thy garment; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the uppermost vest, answerable to a cloak amongst us. God furnishes his people thus with necessaries, and he will have them use them, so far as they are able to serve them, even then when he is working of miracles for their deliverances. ",
        "children": []
